How to create a django project??
django-admin startproject hellodjango

How to create a django app??
python3 manage.py startapp helloworld

#How to start a local django server??
python3 manage.py runserver	0.0.0.0:8081

#How to find you BASE_DIR in django??
>>>from django.conf import settings
>>>settings.BASE_DIR


django-admin.py startproject myproject ~/myprojectdir

python manage.py makemigrations --settings=sst.settings.production
python manage.py createsuperuser --settings=sst.settings.production
python manage.py runserver --settings=sst.settings.production